"title": "8470: respect, for God's character",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8470: respect, for god's character",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's revelation of himself calls for deference, honour and a response of right living.</p>\n<h2>Respect for God's name</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:2\">PSA 29:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:11\">DEU 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20-Exod23:21\">EXO 23:20–23:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev18:21\">LEV 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:12\">LEV 19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:31-Lev22:33\">LEV 22:31–22:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:10-Lev24:16\">LEV 24:10–24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:9-Ps86:11\">PSA 86:9–86:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:16-Jer3:17\">JER 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:1-Mal2:2\">MAL 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for God's presence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:5-Exod3:6\">EXO 3:5–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19-Exod33:23\">EXO 33:19–33:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:7\">PSA 89:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:5\">ISA 6:1–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:7\">ZEP 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:13\">ZEC 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for God's word</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:2\">DEU 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:32\">DEU 12:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:7-Josh1:8\">JOS 1:7–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:5-Prov30:6\">PRO 30:5–30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19-2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:19–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:18-Rev22:19\">REV 22:18–22:19</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for God's ark and sanctuary</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:30\">LEV 19:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:19-1Sam6:20\">1SA 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:1-2Sam6:7\">2SA 6:1–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:1-Eccl5:2\">ECC 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:20\">HAB 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12-Matt21:13\">MAT 21:12–21:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:15-Mark11:17\">MRK 11:15–11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:45-Luke19:46\">LUK 19:45–19:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:13-John2:17\">JHN 2:13–2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:11\">JER 7:11</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for God's servants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:12-1Thess5:13\">1TH 5:12–5:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:1-Acts23:5\">ACT 23:1–23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:28\">EXO 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:7-Acts28:10\">ACT 28:7–28:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:29-Phil2:30\">PHP 2:29–2:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17-1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:17–5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:7\">HEB 13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></p>\n<h2>Respect for God leads to godly living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:20\">EXO 20:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:30-2Chr6:31\">2CH 6:30–6:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:6\">PRO 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:7\">HEB 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:14-1Pet1:17\">1PE 1:14–1:17</a></p>",
